trenchment he highlighted several practical policy solutions from japan that the european union should consider such as the top runner program for energy efficiency in addition lipscy warned that european policymakers should avoid repeating the mistakes of japan's lost decade by responding to the euro crisis quickly and decisively search aparc search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest japanese policymakers struggle over nuclear power question daniel c sneider yaleglobal online on october 5 2011 conference compares wartime experiences in asia and europe video+ august 22 2011 news phillip y lipscy among us japan network for the future fellows at june policymakers meetings july 23 2010 press release shorenstein aparc delegation visits chinese scholars policymakers and business leaders july 29 2007 news new power dynamics in southeast asia issues for us policymakers conference report published may 31 2007 seaf news three groundbreaking stanford alumni to share their experiences and insights on entrepreneurship in china february 12 2007 sprie announcement support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 9741 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
